  "detailed_description": "<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/2fe98954480c2fc830b5eabcde0e5399.avif?t=1722624582\" width=620 height=72 /></span><br>Farm! Fish! Sail! Do magic! Fall in love? You can do all this and more in Spellfield, the fantasy RPG. Fulfill the Ancient Prophecy, if you dare...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Farm!</h2>Cultivate your land - clear the earth, plant seeds, water them, and harvest!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/54ec3f7374564d7004b6f966bedc9800.poster.avif?t=1722624582\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/54ec3f7374564d7004b6f966bedc9800.webm?t=1722624582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/54ec3f7374564d7004b6f966bedc9800.mp4?t=1722624582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fish!</h2>Find rare fish and improve your skills!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/8345f5435c2f9e9cca38a2ec63462bc7.poster.avif?t=1722624582\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/8345f5435c2f9e9cca38a2ec63462bc7.webm?t=1722624582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/8345f5435c2f9e9cca38a2ec63462bc7.mp4?t=1722624582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sail!</h2>Navigate the high seas around Spellfield and sail to distant lands!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/f2da1a212ef0e127fd58150508b27e39.poster.avif?t=1722624582\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/f2da1a212ef0e127fd58150508b27e39.webm?t=1722624582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/f2da1a212ef0e127fd58150508b27e39.mp4?t=1722624582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do Magic!</h2>Become a master of magic - use powerful staffs, cloaks, and rings!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/9f3d790f15c5e47b43d0c819e6a153c6.poster.avif?t=1722624582\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/9f3d790f15c5e47b43d0c819e6a153c6.webm?t=1722624582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/9f3d790f15c5e47b43d0c819e6a153c6.mp4?t=1722624582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fall in Love?</h2>Befriend the townsfolk and find romance!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/c8dce8a2a43fa011333a01538d97af27.poster.avif?t=1722624582\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/c8dce8a2a43fa011333a01538d97af27.webm?t=1722624582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404020/extras/c8dce8a2a43fa011333a01538d97af27.mp4?t=1722624582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features List:<br>-Explore a richly detailed world<br>-Befriend the townsfolk<br>-Learn seven skills: Farming, Forestry, Mining, Fishing, Combat, Stealth and Magic!<br>-Have cute pets and take care of them<br>-Plumb the depths of vast dungeons<br>-Create useful machines and cook food<br>-Play many Mini-games and solve puzzles<br>-Use magic equipment to offer special bonuses<br>-Learn lore and secrets from in-game books<br>-Witness the changing seasons and dynamic world<br>-Attend the town festivals through the year<br>-Over an hour of OST!<br>-Collect various items to unlock sweet bonuses around town<br>-Uncover the many secrets of Spellfield...",
